name: Boba Fett (V)
Lore: 'Infamous bounty hunter. Hired to help Jabba intimidate debtors and smugglers. Crack shot. Mandalorian armor and jet pack provide protection and flight capability.',
Text: 'Adds 3 to power of anything he pilots.  May ''fly'' (landspeed = 3).  Permanent weapon is Projectile Grappling Hook (may target a character for free; draw destiny; target captured if destiny +1 > defense value).  Immune to attrition < 3 (< 5 while with Jabba).(Errata Text - September 9th, 2009)',
